{"tid":1977103,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【黃色音樂圈】無力感 - 許廷鏗","createTime":"2020-04-17T16:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T15:29:35.000Z","uid":230581,"like":52,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a5ae01e8dc4090c6a70ab59ec09d937153311e8b","tid":1977103,"uid":230581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T16:55:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hm0VCDzJSg4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fhm0VCDzJSg4&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppeiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=934971b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hm0VCDzJSg4</a><br />\n<br />\n如出走 烏托邦再<br />\n無以後 得你跟我<br />\n同死守 雖滿佈傷口<br />\n仍可跟劫數爭鬥<br />\n如失守 只要跟你<br />\n留最後 這晚終長<br />\n留千秋 英勇抹不走<br />\n絕境中更罕有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌詞:<br />\n滴汗 滴盡換來是刺痛<br />\n熾熱過的失望 比冰水更凍<br />\n願望 望極未尋獲答案<br />\n看盡再多黑夜 亦是沒光芒<br />\n<br />\n衝不開揮不走 軀體沾滿血垢<br />\n若是所有難受 一個人善後<br />\n無力站在最後<br />\n<br />\n如出走 身處死角<br />\n逃不走 走遍低處<br />\n無出口 只有這傷口<br />\n和身邊每句呼救<br />\n齊出手 組個攻勢<br />\n來堅守 跟我一搏<br />\n毋退後 轉眼會失守<br />\n才必須要拯救<br />\n來一起去拯救<br />\n<br />\n絕望 獨自沒能力搏鬥<br />\n聽集結的響號 力量便交投<br />\n<br />\n史詩式的畫面 不需精美刺繡<br />\n就是心血掏盡 彈斷糧絕後<br />\n同屹立在最後<br />\n<br />\n如出走 身處死角<br />\n逃不走 走遍低處<br />\n無出口 只有這傷口<br />\n和身邊每句呼救<br />\n齊出手 組個攻勢<br />\n來堅守 跟我一搏<br />\n毋退後 早晚會失守<br />\n仍必須要拯救<br />\n<br />\n誰有過對立與嗟怨<br />\n來到了這晚亦看穿<br />\n如今一體生死置於一線<br />\n獨自活著未能自處<br />\n來交出瑟縮的兩手<br />\n同為著活著並肩抵擋這詛咒<br />\n如不想失救就合力自救<br />\n未懼命運就用力纏鬥<br />\n<br />\n如出走 烏托邦再<br />\n無以後 得你跟我<br />\n同死守 雖滿佈傷口<br />\n仍可跟劫數爭鬥<br />\n如失守 只要跟你<br />\n留最後 這晚終長<br />\n留千秋 英勇抹不走<br />\n絕境中更罕有"},{"pid":"939b6b05c7141b369c14cee8df8b272f9e49528c","tid":1977103,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:07:23.000Z","msg":"許生<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">香 港 國 寶 ： 許冠傑<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1973620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1973620</a></div>"},{"pid":"5f62b9399e7c04cb07be575d4d7c284c5d52b8ae","tid":1977103,"uid":117237,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:17:34.000Z","msg":"真心唔知咩原來後庭係黃咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916b88f5a932ec688badbfd148aef527c8fae30e","tid":1977103,"uid":55960,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:57:27.000Z","msg":"依首歌唔係講自己咩 之前睇佢IG好頹咁"},{"pid":"9c1bc7438eeb4dbfa1802f9ab029abaa9ab8bdd2","tid":1977103,"uid":98117,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:32:10.000Z","msg":"點解咁多負評？我幾支持首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad05c48c2ee01899a027952102ac184d9cd5613f","tid":1977103,"uid":340305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T20:36:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b47a9f29528f7c03223fdc4e7eda9d7d29d824a1","tid":1977103,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"5f62b9399e7c04cb07be575d4d7c284c5d52b8ae","tid":1977103,"uid":117237,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:17:34.000Z","msg":"真心唔知咩原來後庭係黃咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T22:00:20.000Z","msg":"暗黃啦我會歸類為<br />\n不過首歌啲詞又真係幾激勵人心嘅"},{"pid":"98104cca8fdd136d70b1e61457d06f4474bfc22a","tid":1977103,"uid":230511,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b47a9f29528f7c03223fdc4e7eda9d7d29d824a1","tid":1977103,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"5f62b9399e7c04cb07be575d4d7c284c5d52b8ae","tid":1977103,"uid":117237,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17